data.name: Carrot Sticks with Ranch Dip
data.quickTastyDescription: Crispy carrot sticks paired with creamy ranch dip for a refreshing snack.
detailedCookingInstructions: Cut the carrots into sticks (about 4 inches long).
Place the carrot sticks in a serving bowl.
Pour ranch dressing into a small bowl for dipping.
data.detailedName: Crispy Carrot Sticks with Creamy Ranch Dip
